responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "BFA5D355461BA25598B721A1F919256C", "Hordes from the the Void brought with them death. Many did fall with the Bull\'s last breath. - Many did fall to the Bull that day. But in the end it was not his fray. - Betrayed and to bones his corpse did rot. Monks from afar brought honor long sought. - So did rise a lonely shrine. With pyre to raise ashes high. - Sing aloud all sons of the horn. Sing aloud the curse and ever mourn.")
name: MIDD_0017_TLS_Tablet_TheBalladOfTheBull_15
